title: Campaigning
new-page: true
view-if: not rubicon or campaigning_timer <= 0
on-arrival: month_actions += 1; campaigning_timer +=2 if rubicon
max-visits: 36
is-card: true
card-image: img/erc/campaign.jpeg
face-image: img/erc/campaign.jpeg
frequency: 100
tags: erc_party

= Campaigning

Whether or not we are in an electoral campaign, the party is always trying to broaden its voter base. Who should we focus our campaign efforts on?

- @workers: The industrial working class, including factory workers, construction workers, and service workers.
- @redbelt: The working class in the metropolitan area of Barcelona, the traditional stronghold of the PSC.
- @middle: The middle working class of professionals, public employees, and highly qualified workers.
- @business: Small business owners and the self-employed.
- @rural: Rural workers and small farmers from rural Catalonia.
- @unemployed: The unemployed.
- @root: We either don't want to or cannot campaign right now.
- @easy_discard

@workers
subtitle: -1 resources
choose-if: party_resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
on-arrival: {!
    Q.erc_parlament_barcelona_ind_support += (1-Q.erc_dissent/100); 
    Q.erc_parlament_girona_ind_support += 6*(1-Q.erc_dissent/100);
    Q.erc_parlament_lleida_ind_support += 6*(1-Q.erc_dissent/100);
    Q.erc_parlament_tarragona_ind_support += 2*(1-Q.erc_dissent/100);
    Q.party_resources -= 1; 
    if (Q.unemployment >= 20 && (Q.erc_supporting == 1 || Q.erc_in_gob == 1)) {
        Q.erc_parlament_barcelona_ind_support -= 1;
        Q.erc_parlament_girona_ind_support -= 1;
        Q.erc_parlament_lleida_ind_support -= 1;
        Q.erc_parlament_tarragona_ind_support -= 1;
    }
    if (Q.broken_roadmap == 1) {
        Q.erc_parlament_barcelona_ind_support -= 4;
        Q.erc_parlament_girona_ind_support -= 4;
        Q.erc_parlament_lleida_ind_support -= 4;
        Q.erc_parlament_tarragona_ind_support -= 2;
    }
!}

We have increased our campaigning among industrial workers across Catalonia, but such a generalized campaign will have a hard time breaking through Barcelona's red belt. [? if gabriel_rufian_advisor: The figure of Gabriel Rufian seems to be functioning greatly for these campaigns. ?][? if unemployed >= 20 and (erc_supporting = 1 or erc_in_gob = 1): The high levels of unemployment make our campaign more difficult, since we are associated with the government that enacted cuts, and our campaign may even backfire. ?][? if broken_roadmap = 1: We have been unable to follow through with our roadmap to independence, and that makes our campaign more notoriously more difficult. ?]

@redbelt
subtitle: -1 resources
view-if: gabriel_rufian_advisor = 1 or erc_break_red_belt = 1
choose-if: party_resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
on-arrival: {!
    Q.erc_parlament_barcelona_ind_support += 6*(1-Q.erc_dissent/100) + 2*Q.gabriel_rufian_advisor; 
    Q.erc_parlament_tarragona_ind_support += 4*(1-Q.erc_dissent/100) + Q.gabriel_rufian_advisor;
    Q.party_resources -= 1; 
    if (Q.unemployment >= 20 && (Q.erc_supporting == 1 || Q.erc_in_gob == 1)) {
        Q.erc_parlament_barcelona_ind_support -= 1;
        Q.erc_parlament_tarragona_ind_support -= 1;
    }
    if (Q.broken_roadmap == 1) {
        Q.erc_parlament_barcelona_ind_support -= 4;
        Q.erc_parlament_tarragona_ind_support -= 2;
    }
!}

We have increased our campaigning efforts among industrial workers, specially around Barcelona's red belt, the traditional stronghold of the PSC. [? if gabriel_rufian_advisor: The figure of Gabriel Rufian seems to be functioning greatly for these campaigns. ?][? if unemployed >= 20 and (erc_supporting = 1 or erc_in_gob = 1): The high levels of unemployment make our campaign more difficult, since we are associated with the government that enacted cuts, and our campaign may even backfire. ?][? if broken_roadmap = 1: We have been unable to follow through with our roadmap to independence, and that makes our campaign more notoriously more difficult. ?]

@middle
subtitle: -1 resources
choose-if: party_resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
on-arrival: {!
    Q.erc_parlament_barcelona_middle_support += 6*(1-Q.erc_dissent/100) + Q.joan_josep_nuet_advisor + Q.joan_laporta_advisor;
    Q.erc_parlament_girona_middle_support += 6*(1-Q.erc_dissent/100) + Q.raul_romeva_advisor;
    Q.erc_parlament_lleida_middle_support += 6*(1-Q.erc_dissent/100) + Q.raul_romeva_advisor;
    Q.erc_parlament_tarragona_middle_support += 6*(1-Q.erc_dissent/100);
    Q.party_resources -= 1;
    if (Q.unemployment >= 20 && (Q.erc_supporting == 1 || Q.erc_in_gob == 1)) {
        Q.erc_parlament_barcelona_middle_support -= 1;
        Q.erc_parlament_girona_middle_support -= 1;
        Q.erc_parlament_lleida_middle_support -= 1;
        Q.erc_parlament_tarragona_middle_support -= 1;
    }
    if (Q.broken_roadmap == 1) {
        Q.erc_parlament_barcelona_middle_support -= 4;
        Q.erc_parlament_girona_middle_support -= 4;
        Q.erc_parlament_lleida_middle_support -= 4;
        Q.erc_parlament_tarragona_middle_support -= 4;
    }
!}

We have increased our campaigning among the middle class. [? if unemployed >= 20 and (erc_supporting = 1 or erc_in_gob = 1): The high levels of unemployment make our campaign more difficult, since we are associated with the government that enacted cuts, and our campaign may even backfire. ?][? if broken_roadmap = 1: We have been unable to follow through with our roadmap to independence, and that makes our campaign more notoriously more difficult. ?]

@business
subtitle: -1 resources
choose-if: party_resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
on-arrival: {!
    Q.erc_parlament_barcelona_business_support += (Q.erc_pragmatic_strength/100)*(1-Q.erc_dissent/100) + Q.joan_laporta_advisor; 
    Q.erc_parlament_girona_business_support += (Q.erc_pragmatic_strength/100)*(1-Q.erc_dissent/100) + Q.joan_laporta_advisor;
    Q.erc_parlament_lleida_business_support += (Q.erc_pragmatic_strength/100)*(1-Q.erc_dissent/100) + Q.joan_laporta_advisor;
    Q.erc_parlament_tarragona_business_support += (Q.erc_pragmatic_strength/100)*(1-Q.erc_dissent/100) + Q.joan_laporta_advisor;
    Q.party_resources -= 1; 
    if (Q.broken_roadmap == 1) {
        Q.erc_parlament_barcelona_business_support -= 1;
        Q.erc_parlament_girona_business_support -= 1;
        Q.erc_parlament_lleida_business_support -= 1;
        Q.erc_parlament_tarragona_business_support -= 1;
    }
    if (Q.erc_roadmap > 2) {
        Q.erc_parlament_barcelona_business_support -= 2;
        Q.erc_parlament_girona_business_support -= 2;
        Q.erc_parlament_lleida_business_support -= 2;
        Q.erc_parlament_tarragona_business_support -= 2;
    }
!}

We have increased our campaigning among the business community. [? if erc_pragmatic_strength < 40 or erc_roadmap > 2: However, our general party lines are not the most appealing to this group, who may prefer more pragmatic approaches to politics. ?][? if broken_roadmap = 1: We have been unable to follow through with our roadmap to independence, and that makes our campaign somewhat more difficult. ?]

