        Q.erc_parlament_girona_rural_support -= 6;
        Q.erc_parlament_lleida_rural_support -= 6;
        Q.erc_parlament_tarragona_rural_support -= 6;
    }
    if (Q.broken_roadmap == 1) {
        Q.erc_parlament_barcelona_rural_support -= 8;
        Q.erc_parlament_girona_rural_support -= 8;
        Q.erc_parlament_lleida_rural_support -= 8;
        Q.erc_parlament_tarragona_rural_support -= 8;
    }

!}

We have increased our campaigning efforts in rural Catalonia. [? if unemployment >= 20 and (erc_supporting = 1 or erc_in_gob = 1): The high levels of unemployment make our campaign more difficult, since we are associated with the government that enacted cuts, and our campaign may even backfire. ?][? if broken_roadmap = 1: We have been unable to follow through with our roadmap to independence, and that makes our campaign specially difficult. ?]

